<P>
BUCHAREST, February 11 (Xinhua) -- Private kindergarten and
schools are rapidly expanding in Romania, with 72 private
kindergartens and 113 private schools opened so far, the Rompres
news agency Thursday quoted sources from the Ministry of National
Education as saying.
</P>
