It is worthy of note that special methods for teaching foreign
languages were introduced in private schools. These units take
into account the children's options for certain disciplines as
well as their gifts. Syllabuses are elaborated which pay attention
to these elements. Teachers are chosen on the basis of tests.
</P>
<P>
According to sources from the Ministry of National Education,
notable results have been scored so far in private schools.
