Haidong found the net twice to help four-time Chinese league
champion Dalian Wanda beat Jubilo Iwata of Japan 2-0 in a quarter-
final group match of the Asian club championship on Friday.
</P>
<P>
Dalian, defending runner-up for the tournament, went two points
clear in the east Asian quarter-final group.
</P>
<P>
