Nemecek's pass with the right foot and blasted with the left the
ball into the net from 20 meters.
</P>
<P>
In the all South Korean match, Pohang striker Park Sang-in
tapped in from close range in the 15th minute from a perfect pass
by captain Park Tae-ha.
</P>
<P>
