<HEADLINE> Christie to Run in Dortmund </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, February 12 (Xinhua) -- Former Olympic 100 meters
champion Linford Christie of Britain has recovered from the
hamstring injury and will run in Dortmund on Saturday night.
</P>
