medalist Christian Malcolm and 1996 European indoor champion Marc
Blume of Germany.
</P>
<P>
Christie, third at a meeting in Sweden earlier won by Britain's
current number one 60m star Jason Gardener, is still insisting he
has no intentions of competing in major international
championships. 
