about lasting peace in Mindanao so that its residents can finally
have the fruits of the progress.
</P>
<P>
He said his week-long visit will reinforce his administration's
commitment to focusing attention on the south and "show our
brother Muslims that we are sincere, we are determined to give
priority to the development of Mindanao."
</P>
<P>
Estrada has pledged to transform Mindanao into the country's
food basket by developing its agriculture sector and launching
several food security programs in the south. 
