opening 12 minutes as Atlanta shot a sizzling 74 percent from the
floor and held Charlotte to 27 percent.
</P>
<P>
Derrick Coleman had 17 points and 13 rebounds for the Hornets,
who fell to 1-4 with star forwards Glen Rice and Anthony Mason out
of the lineup. 
